According to Article 19 of the Law No. 152-FZ, the data operator should take all reasonable organizational and technical measures when processing personal data in order to prevent unauthorized access to personal data, its destruction, alteration, blocking, copying, distribution or conduct of other illegitimate acts. 
Article 22.1 of the Law which has been in force since 2011 requires appointment of a person responsible for organizing the processing of personal data. This person is responsible for organizing the processing of personal data and should:
